#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

exec claude --model opus --permission-mode auto \
  "$(cat <<'EOF'
You are running an autonomous work session. Execute these two phases in order:

## Phase 1: /work
Immediately invoke the /work skill. This will:
1. Pick the next bug or story from the active Notion sprint
2. Implement it (plan, code, test)
3. Ship it (commit, push, open PR, verify CI, address review)
4. Update Notion statuses

## Phase 2: /complete (after PR merge)
Once the PR has been merged, invoke the /complete skill. This will:
1. Verify the PR is merged
2. Move the Notion story to Done (or bug to Fixed)
3. Switch back to main and pull latest

Begin now by invoking /work.
EOF
)"
